Oh, boy. I can't tell
which one is real.

00:06:31.091 --> 00:06:33.727
[EXERTION]

00:06:33.727 --> 00:06:36.830
Bubble.
[BUBBLE MOVE]

00:06:36.830 --> 00:06:40.200
[PAINED]

