Fennekin is unable to battle.
So the winner is Ash.

00:06:42.302 --> 00:06:43.837
[EXERTION]

00:06:43.837 --> 00:06:44.971
Thanks, Froakie. Return.

00:06:44.971 --> 00:06:47.941
[HAPPY]

00:06:47.941 --> 00:06:50.810
You battled well.
Take a nice rest, okay?

00:06:52.812 --> 00:06:55.048
Serena?

00:06:55.048 --> 00:06:58.451
Now will you believe
what I told you?

00:06:58.451 --> 00:07:01.688
I would never lose to the Ash
I know so I have to.

00:07:01.688 --> 00:07:03.890
I guess you're Ash
from another world.

00:07:03.890 --> 00:07:05.258
Glad that's settled.

00:07:05.258 --> 00:07:06.459
So where's the crybaby Ash

00:07:06.459 --> 00:07:07.627
we're all familiar with?

00:07:07.627 --> 00:07:09.629
Here I am.

00:07:09.629 --> 00:07:12.632
[gasps]

00:07:12.632 --> 00:07:15.235
[EXCITED]

00:07:15.235 --> 00:07:18.238
It appears
there are two of them.

00:07:18.238 --> 00:07:20.006
Pikachu.

00:07:20.006 --> 00:07:21.574
Buddy, I was so worried.

00:07:21.574 --> 00:07:23.310
[HAPPY]

