Hey, Ash.
Can you tell me what happened?

00:07:26.780 --> 00:07:29.082
Sure.

00:07:29.082 --> 00:07:31.985
It was after
my battle with Serena.

00:07:31.985 --> 00:07:33.520
Froakie is unable to battle.

