without thinking.

00:08:01.848 --> 00:08:04.384
Then I saw a cave
so I ran inside.

00:08:06.886 --> 00:08:11.291
But all of a sudden,
I got lost.

00:08:11.291 --> 00:08:13.159
And the next thing I knew,
Pikachu was gone.

00:08:13.159 --> 00:08:15.595
Pikachu. Where are you?

00:08:16.963 --> 00:08:18.331
Pikachu!

00:08:21.968 --> 00:08:23.370
Huh?

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:25.605
Pikachu. Huh?

00:08:25.605 --> 00:08:26.773
Pikachu.

00:08:27.974 --> 00:08:30.110
[CONFUSED] / [PANIC]

00:08:30.110 --> 00:08:32.479
Thank goodness.

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:35.915
But after that I realized
it wasn't my Pikachu.

00:08:35.915 --> 00:08:38.585
I'm really, really sorry.

00:08:38.585 --> 00:08:41.688
No prob. I've got my Pikachu
back and that's what counts.

00:08:41.688 --> 00:08:43.456
[AGREEMENT]

00:08:43.456 --> 00:08:45.859
Strange things happen,
I suppose.

00:08:45.859 --> 00:08:48.895
Wow. That's kinda confusing.

00:08:48.895 --> 00:08:50.663
Hey, you know what would be
awesome if you'd tell me

00:08:50.663 --> 00:08:53.633
a little bit about your Pikachu.

00:08:53.633 --> 00:08:55.902
To tell the truth,
my Pikachu's tough.

00:08:55.902 --> 00:08:58.671
Wild and aggressive.

00:08:58.671 --> 00:09:01.241
[screaming]

00:09:01.241 --> 00:09:03.243
[MOCKING]

00:09:03.243 --> 00:09:04.711
Your volts will be no good
in this globe.

00:09:05.912 --> 00:09:08.314
[IRON TAIL MOVE]

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:11.851
[gasps]
Huh?

00:09:11.851 --> 00:09:14.854
[MOCKING]

00:09:14.854 --> 00:09:16.022
JESSIE
'Why you..'

00:09:16.022 --> 00:09:17.390
[CONCERN]

00:09:17.390 --> 00:09:20.894
'Gotcha.'
[FRUSTRATED]

00:09:20.894 --> 00:09:23.329
Is this the same Pikachu
we know and love?

00:09:23.329 --> 00:09:25.265
We saw this rascal
with the Twerp

00:09:25.265 --> 00:09:26.332
and there can only
be one of him.

00:09:26.332 --> 00:09:29.602
[AGREEMENT]

00:09:29.602 --> 00:09:32.839
I can't just leave you hanging
when you're in trouble.

00:09:32.839 --> 00:09:35.375
I'll tell you what. I'm gonna
help you find your Pikachu.

00:09:35.375 --> 00:09:36.776
