when to quit!

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:35.728
Yep. What a waste of watts.

00:11:36.863 --> 00:11:39.365
Hm. Company.

00:11:39.365 --> 00:11:41.701
We'd better make
our bad selves scarce.

00:11:41.701 --> 00:11:43.603
[panting]

00:11:43.603 --> 00:11:46.472
‐ Ah.
‐ It's a dead end.

00:11:46.472 --> 00:11:48.708
Now, where in the world
is that Pikachu?

00:11:48.708 --> 00:11:50.376
Wish I knew.

00:11:50.376 --> 00:11:52.445
Even brother dear
makes mistakes.

00:11:54.581 --> 00:11:56.916
Who knew the Twerp had a twin.

00:11:56.916 --> 00:11:59.719
MEOWTH
'With another Pikachu in tow.'

00:11:59.719 --> 00:12:01.588
This situation's starting
to make my hair hurt.

00:12:01.588 --> 00:12:02.989
Your hair?

00:12:02.989 --> 00:12:04.724
Can the kvetching for later

00:12:04.724 --> 00:12:06.960
and let's grab
that Pikachu for now.

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:09.562
You can't have too many,
I always say.

