00:12:15.201 --> 00:12:16.936
I'll, I'll,
I'll never be the same!

00:12:16.936 --> 00:12:18.805
[gasps]

00:12:18.805 --> 00:12:20.974
Just perfect.
Here we go.

00:12:20.974 --> 00:12:22.342
Come on, Ash, don't cry.

00:12:22.342 --> 00:12:24.611
[ENCOURAGING]

00:12:24.611 --> 00:12:26.346
You wanna find Pikachu,
don't you?

00:12:26.346 --> 00:12:28.748
‐ Mm‐hm.
‐ Okay, don't give up.

00:12:28.748 --> 00:12:29.515
[ENCOURAGING]

00:12:30.383 --> 00:12:32.018
[whimpering]

00:12:33.152 --> 00:12:34.220
[SHOCK]

00:12:36.356 --> 00:12:38.424
‐ Perfect aim.
‐ Hey, what?

00:12:38.424 --> 00:12:41.127
Prepare for trouble.
Hey, what or not.

00:12:41.127 --> 00:12:43.630
And make it double.
You can see what we've got.

00:12:43.630 --> 00:12:46.132
To protect the world
from devastation.

00:12:46.132 --> 00:12:48.768
To unite all people
within our nation.

00:12:48.768 --> 00:12:51.771
To denounce the evils
of a Twerpish twin.

00:12:51.771 --> 00:12:53.406
To extend our reach
to the stars that spin.

00:12:54.907 --> 00:12:57.744
‐ Jessie.
‐ And James.

00:12:57.744 --> 00:13:00.647
Team Rocket blasts off
at the speed of light.

00:13:00.647 --> 00:13:02.715
Surrender now or prepare
yourselves for a fight.

00:13:02.715 --> 00:13:04.384
Meowth! That's right!

00:13:04.384 --> 00:13:05.685
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:13:08.521 --> 00:13:10.657
Team Rocket!
Not you again.

00:13:10.657 --> 00:13:11.457
BOTH
Team Rocket?

00:13:11.457 --> 00:13:13.259
Uh‐huh.

00:13:13.259 --> 00:13:14.427
They're a bunch
of really bad guys

00:13:14.427 --> 00:13:16.462
who steal
other people's Pokémon.

00:13:16.462 --> 00:13:19.565
Huh? Our Team Rocket folks
call themselves

00:13:19.565 --> 00:13:21.934
the heroes of justic.
They beat up bad guys.

00:13:21.934 --> 00:13:24.037
‐ Huh? Heroes of justice?
‐ Huh?

00:13:24.037 --> 00:13:27.340
[STRUGGLING]

00:13:27.340 --> 00:13:29.642
‐ Hey, Ash. That's my Pikachu.
‐ What?

00:13:29.642 --> 00:13:31.010
So, you're a bad Team Rocket?

00:13:31.010 --> 00:13:32.845
[ANGRY]

00:13:32.845 --> 00:13:35.415
Now, look.
Give us back our Pikachu!

00:13:35.415 --> 00:13:37.083
Sure. Soon as you grow up!

00:13:37.083 --> 00:13:38.351
It's show time.

00:13:38.351 --> 00:13:41.020
[APPEARING]

00:13:41.020 --> 00:13:43.089
‐ Hey, Ash. Let's go.
‐ Hm.

00:13:43.089 --> 00:13:44.290
BOTH
I choose you.

00:13:44.290 --> 00:13:46.225
[APPEARING]

00:13:47.794 --> 00:13:50.263
BOTH
You chose Hawlucha too?

00:13:50.263 --> 00:13:51.764
‐ Use Karate Chop on Inkay.
‐ Use Karate Chop on Pumpkaboo.

00:13:51.764 --> 00:13:54.033
[KARATE CHOP MOVE]

00:13:54.033 --> 00:13:55.935
[PAINED]

00:13:55.935 --> 00:13:57.837
[NERVOUS]

00:14:01.140 --> 00:14:02.608
[gasps]
Hawlucha, look out!

00:14:02.608 --> 00:14:04.477
[EXERTION]

00:14:04.477 --> 00:14:06.045
Hawlucha.

00:14:06.045 --> 00:14:07.880
[STRUGGLING]
Inkay, Psybeam!

00:14:07.880 --> 00:14:09.615
[PSYBEAM MOVE]

00:14:09.615 --> 00:14:11.184
[EXERTION]

00:14:11.184 --> 00:14:12.485
Hawlucha!

00:14:12.485 --> 00:14:15.488
[PAINED]

00:14:15.488 --> 00:14:19.459
Hawlucha's confused.
Alright, return.

00:14:19.459 --> 00:14:21.461
I'm sorry, Hawlucha.

00:14:21.461 --> 00:14:22.995
Alright, Shadow Ball.

00:14:22.995 --> 00:14:24.864
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]

00:14:24.864 --> 00:14:26.599
[PAINED]

00:14:26.599 --> 00:14:29.035
[groaning]

00:14:29.035 --> 00:14:30.770
Are you okay, Ash?

00:14:30.770 --> 00:14:33.106
Yeah. No good.

00:14:33.106 --> 00:14:34.607
Looks like I'm finished.

00:14:35.775 --> 00:14:38.878
[crying]

00:14:38.878 --> 00:14:40.913
Come on. Your crying
isn't gonna do you any good.

00:14:42.815 --> 00:14:45.184
Yeah. We haven't
lost anything yet.

00:14:45.184 --> 00:14:46.719
There's no reason
to give up.

00:14:48.955 --> 00:14:50.823
Okay. I hear you.

00:14:52.492 --> 00:14:54.927
[STRUGGLING]

00:14:54.927 --> 00:14:56.596
Huh? Huh.

00:14:56.596 --> 00:14:58.531
Huh?

00:14:58.531 --> 00:15:01.734
Look, Twerp,
what're you doin'?

00:15:01.734 --> 00:15:02.769
Now, you're done.
No, you don't.

00:15:02.769 --> 00:15:05.304
[PANIC]

00:15:05.304 --> 00:15:06.773
‐ Clemont.
‐ Hm.

00:15:06.773 --> 00:15:08.074
That's my big brother.

00:15:08.074 --> 00:15:10.510
Here goes. Ha!

00:15:10.510 --> 00:15:12.712
[SCARED]

00:15:12.712 --> 00:15:15.681
Leave the rest to me.
Fennekin, your turn.

00:15:15.681 --> 00:15:18.284
[APPEARING]

00:15:19.786 --> 00:15:21.421
[RELIEVED]

00:15:21.421 --> 00:15:23.890
[FOCUSED]

00:15:23.890 --> 00:15:25.291
Let's wrap it up.
Ready, Ash?

00:15:25.291 --> 00:15:27.960
Okay. If you say so, Ash.

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:30.596
BOTH
Pikachu. Thunderbolt, let's go.

00:15:30.596 --> 00:15:33.099
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:15:34.901 --> 00:15:37.236
ASH
We're blasting off again!

00:15:37.236 --> 00:15:38.638
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:15:40.840 --> 00:15:43.142
You were amazing, Ash.

00:15:43.142 --> 00:15:45.445
BONNIE
I was completely impressed.

00:15:45.445 --> 00:15:48.014
I hope you'll consider
continuing our journey together.

00:15:48.014 --> 00:15:49.649
‐ Will you?
‐ Mm‐hm.

00:15:49.649 --> 00:15:51.951
Ash, that's awesome.

00:15:51.951 --> 00:15:53.319
Don't forget,
I owe it all to you.

00:15:57.890 --> 00:15:59.625
Let's head on over
to the Pokémon Center.

00:15:59.625 --> 00:16:01.160
'It's gonna be dark soon.'

00:16:03.696 --> 00:16:06.332
"Dark soon."
Huh. How could I forget?

00:16:06.332 --> 00:16:08.468
According to the legend

00:16:08.468 --> 00:16:09.902
people who come
from another world

00:16:09.902 --> 00:16:11.771
can't go back
once the sun sets.

00:16:11.771 --> 00:16:12.672
[SHOCK]

00:16:14.907 --> 00:16:17.076
Here.

00:16:17.076 --> 00:16:19.178
As soon as this mirror
started to waver

00:16:19.178 --> 00:16:21.380
that's when I was able
to go right into it.

00:16:21.380 --> 00:16:22.648
Let me see.

00:16:22.648 --> 00:16:24.550
I'd say the instability

00:16:24.550 --> 00:16:26.052
of the wavering mirror

00:16:26.052 --> 00:16:27.920
is functioning
as something of a gate

00:16:27.920 --> 00:16:30.456
between this world
and the other one.

00:16:30.456 --> 00:16:33.893
But how do we get this mirror
to do it again?

00:16:33.893 --> 00:16:36.362
I'm not sure. Right before
it started to waver..

00:16:37.263 --> 00:16:38.197
Pikachu.

00:16:41.567 --> 00:16:45.004
That's it. I really wanted
to find Pikachu.

00:16:45.004 --> 00:16:47.273
When I started wishing
really hard for that

00:16:47.273 --> 00:16:48.908
then the mirror wavered.

00:16:48.908 --> 00:16:51.310
Wishing really hard.

00:16:51.310 --> 00:16:54.447
That just might have something
to do with it.

00:16:54.447 --> 00:16:57.183
You really wanna return
to your own world, don't you?

00:16:57.183 --> 00:16:59.285
Yeah. Of course I wanna continue
on my journey

00:16:59.285 --> 00:17:01.487
with Clemont, Serena,
and Bonnie.

00:17:01.487 --> 00:17:04.023
Alright, focus on that thought.

00:17:04.023 --> 00:17:05.825
And if your thoughts
are powerful enough

00:17:05.825 --> 00:17:08.761
our two worlds
might just reconnect!

00:17:08.761 --> 00:17:13.032
Okay. If that's what it takes,
I can do it. Let's go back.

00:17:13.032 --> 00:17:15.201
So we can continue on our
journey with our good friends.

00:17:15.201 --> 00:17:16.135
[AGREEMENT]

00:17:19.906 --> 00:17:22.174
Are we ever gonna
see Ash again?

00:17:22.174 --> 00:17:23.976
Of course, we will, Bonnie.

00:17:23.976 --> 00:17:26.646
Don't even ask that.
Ash is coming back.

00:17:26.646 --> 00:17:29.649
That's right.
And Pikachu too.

00:17:29.649 --> 00:17:31.851
‐ We've gotta hold onto hope.
‐ Hm.

00:17:31.851 --> 00:17:33.185
[AGREEMENT]

00:17:37.290 --> 00:17:40.092
Clemont, Bonnie, Serena..

00:17:42.528 --> 00:17:43.896
[CONFUSED]

00:17:43.896 --> 00:17:45.131
[gasps]

00:17:45.131 --> 00:17:46.499
[SHOCK]

00:17:46.499 --> 00:17:47.500
[gasps]

00:17:49.669 --> 00:17:52.271
‐ It's Ash.
‐ It worked.

00:17:52.271 --> 00:17:55.107
‐ There are two Ashes?
‐ Two of us too.

00:17:55.107 --> 00:17:57.510
There's no time.
We'll explain later.

00:17:57.510 --> 00:17:59.378
Our worlds are starting
to move apart.

00:18:01.781 --> 00:18:04.116
The sun is starting to set.

00:18:04.116 --> 00:18:05.851
The two worlds are connected
by our hopes and dreams.

00:18:05.851 --> 00:18:07.753
[URGING]

00:18:07.753 --> 00:18:10.623
Get with it, Serena,
you need to concentrate

00:18:10.623 --> 00:18:11.857
'on how much you want
to journey with Ash.'

00:18:11.857 --> 00:18:14.527
Huh? Hm. Hm.

00:18:14.527 --> 00:18:16.162
Clemont and Bonnie too!

00:18:16.162 --> 00:18:18.331
Concentrate your thoughts!

00:18:18.331 --> 00:18:19.699
‐ Hey. We'll do it!
‐ We'll do it!

00:18:19.699 --> 00:18:21.834
Clemont, Bonnie, Serena!

00:18:21.834 --> 00:18:24.870
[FOCUSED]
Come back, Ash! Pikachu!

00:18:24.870 --> 00:18:27.173
[grunting]

00:18:31.143 --> 00:18:32.578
[CONFUSED]

00:18:38.618 --> 00:18:39.619
[screaming]

00:18:40.653 --> 00:18:41.954
‐ Hold on.
‐ We've got you.

00:18:41.954 --> 00:18:43.255
‐ Don't let go.
‐ Okay.

00:18:43.255 --> 00:18:44.323
[URGING]

00:18:45.825 --> 00:18:48.027
[grunting]

00:18:52.431 --> 00:18:54.033
[RELIEVED]

00:18:54.967 --> 00:18:56.369
ALL
You're safe.

00:18:56.369 --> 00:18:58.771
Everybody, thank you.

00:18:58.771 --> 00:19:00.072
[GRATEFUL]

00:19:03.909 --> 00:19:06.112
Hey, Ash. You take care.

00:19:06.112 --> 00:19:07.747
Serena,
take care of your Ash, got it?

00:19:07.747 --> 00:19:09.415
Mm‐hm.

00:19:09.415 --> 00:19:11.617
‐ Bye, you guys.
‐ Everybody, stay well.

00:19:11.617 --> 00:19:13.953
I do hope we'll meet again.

00:19:13.953 --> 00:19:15.821
Yeah. I'm looking forward to it.

00:19:15.821 --> 00:19:17.890
Goodbye, other Bonnie.

00:19:17.890 --> 00:19:19.692
ALL
'Bye‐bye.'

00:19:19.692 --> 00:19:20.960
ALL
'Bye‐bye.'

00:19:23.029 --> 00:19:24.196
[clinking]

00:19:26.365 --> 00:19:29.168
You know, I can still
hardly believe it.

00:19:29.168 --> 00:19:32.738
Wow, the other Bonnie said,
"I do hope we'll meet again."

00:19:32.738 --> 00:19:34.640
It is a possibility
that the portal

00:19:34.640 --> 00:19:36.876
will open up again sometime.

00:19:36.876 --> 00:19:38.878
In order to prepare for that,
I'll invent‐‐

00:19:38.878 --> 00:19:40.646
They said
they're all gonna continue

00:19:40.646 --> 00:19:42.915
on their journey together
as friends.

00:19:42.915 --> 00:19:45.451
So let's do that too.
Off to the next Gym.

00:19:45.451 --> 00:19:46.619
[AGREEMENT]

00:19:50.222 --> 00:19:52.725
BONNIE
Ah. What a pretty sunset.

00:19:52.725 --> 00:19:54.627
I think we should locate
a Pokémon Center

00:19:54.627 --> 00:19:56.128
before it gets dark.

00:19:58.497 --> 00:20:00.900
‐ Hey, Ash?
‐ Huh?

00:20:00.900 --> 00:20:03.502
We're gonna stay on our journey
together too, right?

00:20:03.502 --> 00:20:06.272
Of course, we are.
Wouldn't want it any other way.

00:20:06.272 --> 00:20:08.607
[AGREEMENT]
We're a team.

00:20:08.607 --> 00:20:09.942
And we're always going
to be a team.

00:20:09.942 --> 00:20:11.277
[AGREEMENT]

00:20:11.277 --> 00:20:14.413
[laughing]
Hm.

00:20:14.413 --> 00:20:17.683
‐ Come on. Let's hurry, Serena.
‐ Right.

00:20:17.683 --> 00:20:19.085
NARRATOR
Following their strange

00:20:19.085 --> 00:20:20.586
experience in
Reflection Cave

00:20:20.586 --> 00:20:22.755
it's off
to the Pokémon Center

00:20:22.755 --> 00:20:24.857
as our heroes'
journey continues.

00:20:29.795 --> 00:20:33.432
That double Thunderbolt from
those twin Pikachu really stung.

00:20:33.432 --> 00:20:35.367
Two Twerps are two too many.

00:20:35.367 --> 00:20:37.069
What's with this place?

00:20:37.069 --> 00:20:38.304
M‐JESSIE
'What's with this place

00:20:38.304 --> 00:20:39.872
is compassionate might.'

00:20:39.872 --> 00:20:41.040
M‐JAMES
And goodness and caring,

00:20:41.040 --> 00:20:42.608
with mercy and light.

00:20:42.608 --> 00:20:44.510
Heroes of justice,
that's right.

00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:46.178
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:20:46.178 --> 00:20:48.114
ALL
Oh, no!

00:20:48.114 --> 00:20:50.516
[PANIC]

00:20:50.516 --> 00:20:52.184
BOTH
Team Rocket. Good night.

